re til at jeg kan komme tilbake, sa Hallgeir Stokken, med et fast glimt i \u00f8yet."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|sortrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "dc9f8e3af1ee6c4c4ca5d0fabd0ae9daabf55690ee669f690f7e26928a72404c"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-02T01:17:41.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Tidligere avdelingsleder Hallgeir Stokken ved Sentrum politistasjon i Trondheim har opplevd sorgreaksjoner de to gangene har som kreftpasient har reist fra R\u00f8ros Rehabiliteringssenter."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1315213.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Rehab4"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/0091eeed2b415151fc20bc0e0f26352b10c6cf47.jpg?59846928"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Roste kreftarbeidet p\u00e5 R\u00f8ros -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "0091eeed2b415151fc20bc0e0f26352b10c6cf47"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "sortrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "law-government-and-politics"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": "hjelp"}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["r\u00f8ros rehabiliteringssenter", "sentrum", "olavsfestdagene"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "hallgeir stokken"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/sortrondelag"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1315213.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Rehab4"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": 